'''湿婆军'''（शिव सेना，Śīv Senā，{{lang-en|Shiv Sena}}）是[[印度|印度]]的一个[[极右翼|极右翼]][[民族主义|民族主义]]政党，雖然中文媒体多譯為「濕婆軍」或「濕婆神軍黨」，然而Śīv Senā的Śīv實際上指的是[[馬拉塔帝國|馬拉塔帝國]]的[[希瓦吉|希瓦吉大帝]]<ref>{{Cite news|language=zh-tw|url=https://www.thenewslens.com/article/91841|title=與濕婆神無關，卻被中文世界誤譯的印度「濕婆神軍黨」|date=2018-04-05|accessdate=2019-04-21|publisher=關鍵評論|author=劉奇峯|archive-date=2019-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190420180747/https://www.thenewslens.com/article/91841|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|language=en|url=https://www.epw.in/journal/2004/14-15/special-articles/shiv-sena-tiger-many-faces.html|title=Shiv Sena: A Tiger with Many Faces?|date=2004-04-03|accessdate=2019-04-21|publisher=economic and political weekly|author=Suhas Palshikar|archive-date=2019-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190420180758/https://www.epw.in/journal/2004/14-15/special-articles/shiv-sena-tiger-many-faces.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|language=en|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/india/snatching-shivaji-from-shiv-sena-memorial-statue-modi-4449582/|title=Snatching Shivaji from Shiv Sena|date=2016-12-29|accessdate=2019-04-21|publisher=indian express|author=Vishwas Waghmode|archive-date=2019-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190420180751/https://indianexpress.com/article/india/snatching-shivaji-from-shiv-sena-memorial-statue-modi-4449582/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。成立于1966年6月19日，由政治漫畫家{{Link-en|巴爾·撒克里|Bal Thackeray}}（Bal Thackeray）创立<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/comment/virsanghvi/the-uncrowned-king-of-mumbai-bal-thackeray/article1-960794.aspx |title=The uncrowned king of Mumbai: Bal Thackeray |date=2012-11-18 |publisher=www.hindustantimes.com |accessdate=2014-05-20 |archive-date=2014-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140520220233/http://www.hindustantimes.com/comment/virsanghvi/the-uncrowned-king-of-mumbai-bal-thackeray/article1-960794.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该党的宗旨是基于“土地之子”的理念和{{Link-en|印度教民族主义|Hindu nationalism}}。湿婆神军党的信仰——「土地之子」理念认为[[马哈拉施特拉邦|马哈拉施特拉邦]]人应该在这个邦比外来人得到更多的权利。<ref name="Rediff article: sons of the soil, lungi slogan, shakhas, south Indians in 1970, shift to Hindutva, defeat of communists/">{{cite web|url=http://in.rediff.com/election/2004/apr/23espec3.htm|title="Know Your Party: Shiv Sena"|publisher=Rediff.com|accessdate=2006-07-22|archive-date=2012-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120321204106/http://in.rediff.com/election/2004/apr/23espec3.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>不过最近湿婆神军党已经更为强调印度教民族主义。在第13届马哈拉施特拉邦议会选举后的任期內，湿婆神军党曾经统治[[马哈拉施特拉邦|马哈拉施特拉邦]]，現仍是该地区最有影响的印度教民族主义政党之一。在[[2014年印度大選|2014年印度大選]]后成為参政黨與[[右翼|右翼]]的[[印度人民黨|印度人民黨]]聯合執政。

現任党主席[[乌达夫·撒克里|乌达夫·撒克里]]是巴爾·撒克里的兒子。

